comment: Justice for Johnny the ONLY Jack Sparrow
commentable_entity.title: Warner Bro's: Justice for Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Drop has been falsely re-labeled as a wife beater. Despite having copious amounts of evidence against Amber Heard, he lost the defamation lawsuit and was fired from Warner Bro’s Entertainment. I want to see Amber Heard brought to justice and put Johnny BACK IN A JOB!!!

The injustice that Johnny received should not be tolerated! My aim is not to hurt or defile anyone in the process, but to make Amber Heard receive her consequences and learn from them. She may not, but that is for her to decide. Johnny Depp is an amazing actor and should never have been in this position to start with! He has given us many years and numerous memorable characters that are all glued in our minds and filled our hearts as children and adults! Jack Sparrow, Sweeney Todd, Edward Scissorhands, Willy Wonka, The Mad Hatter, Grindelwald, even Rango!

i hope that with enough people recognizing that the outcome of the ordeal was wrong, and should have gone a severely different route. This man was beaten, Verbally Abused, cut, and tortured, only to lose his very solid and evidence packed lawsuit to Amber. 

all I ask is for a moment of your time to sign and share.

comment:
Johnny Depp is one of the most respected, beloved actors in the world. This is what it took to tear him down to the ground: 
1. The perjury of one PROVEN abuser & liar.
2. A story in a tabloid you wouldn’t use to line a cat box.
3. One corrupt and/or compromised judge. 
Terrifying and shameful, this is spitting in the face of true victims of violence. There are MILLIONS of us worldwide fighting for justice. Amber Heard belongs in prison. Johnny Depp deserves SO MUCH better than this.
